longBusinessSummary: Information Analysis Incorporated develops and markets computer applications software systems, programming services, and related software products and automation systems in the United States. The company offers legacy software migration and modernization, and data analytics services; and develops web-based and mobile device solutions, including dynamic electronic forms development and conversion. It also sells third-party software licenses, as well as provides implementation and training, and support and maintenance services. The company was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Fairfax, Virginia.
